=== 0.1.0 2014-05-28
* Online and offline payments.
* Automatic order status management.
* Email notifications on successful purchase.
* Sandbox testing capability.
* Client side validation for credit cards.
* Card validation at Conekta's servers so you don't have to be PCI.
=== 0.1.1 2014-05-29
* Fix email notifications.
* Fix offline payment order status.
=== 0.1.2 2014-06-02
* Update observer logic to support virtual orders.
=== 0.1.3 2014-06-09
* Add support to Magento 1.9.0.1.
=== 0.1.4 2014-06-25
* Add warning and logging if module miss dependencies.
